{
  "stem": "22869.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, sure enough, I found my brother alive, my oldest brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, needless to say, again, we raise our hands in thanks to the Almighty that-- that we met.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Especially that's a double joy, because here-- here we thought that he's dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told me that he's not-- he doesn't want to come back home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He maybe come for a visit, but that's it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There wasn't still the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we decide to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he did come back for a visit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were occupying a German-- some Nazi's home in Munich that they were given by the American authorities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they lived there real nicely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a villa.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- we travelled back home-- tell my brother and my sister, hey, I saw him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know he's alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, now, we can believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's-- so we were planning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, by the time, we decided we were going to leave Czechoslovakia, we're going to go to Germany and eventually make our way to Israel.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we are talking about another year, let's say-- when was Israel declared a country?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think in '48.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was just very close before that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a lot in the talk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The UN was dealing with the stuff and so forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came to Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived in Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I ended up in a day camp-- in a DP camp, rather.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and in that DP camp, I became sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I contacted-- I got TB.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the authorities from the UNRRA-- which was the United Nations Relief and Rehabilitation Administration-- had their doctors and stuff there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took me to a hospital to-- that was that camp name was Leipheim.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
